{"tid":1833934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唱衰蔡英文台男「找數」 派雞排捐人工","createTime":"2020-01-22T06:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T07:14:34.000Z","uid":53026,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c94a01e1a3e8b6ab91047cc807c19d8291ca981","tid":1833934,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"唱衰蔡英文台男「找數」 派雞排捐人工<br />\n12小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200122/large/1579622123_9af4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200122%2Flarge%2F1579622123_9af4.jpg&h=bc70a607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何男（左）與領取雞排的民眾合照。<br />\n<br />\n台灣警政署一名外判司機，在總統大選點票時豪言若總統蔡英文能取得800萬票，就請全台灣人每人一塊雞排，結果蔡得票逾817萬，網民紛紛要其「找數」，逃避一周後惟有宣佈送出600份雞排。他昨日也現出真身並出面道歉，坦言未來在網絡留言會更謹慎，希望爭議趕快結束。<br />\n<br />\n道歉求饒盼告一段落<br />\n<br />\n大選開票當日，警政署何姓約聘司機在網上留言道：「如果菜陰魂（蔡英文）拿到800萬票&hellip;&hellip;我請全台灣人民每人一份雞排&hellip;&hellip;幫我截圖，謝謝。」結果蔡得票逾817萬，創了台灣民選總統以來的最高紀錄。雖然何立刻關閉facebook，但仍被網友起底其身份和職業。何在網上消失一周後，周日（19日）重開facebook，宣佈兩天後將在台北市通化街發放600份雞排，每人限領一份，並反省網絡發言必須謹慎。<br />\n<br />\n昨日接近中午，已有民眾在雞排店外排隊，等着領取號碼牌，到預告派發雞排的下午5時半現場人龍已綿延逾一公里。由於雞排份數過多，店家根本忙不過來，職員只得叫民眾別再排隊。發放雞排時，何男出面致歉，也大方地與領到雞排的民眾合影。他強調，針對這件事情所衍生出的風波，感到十分抱歉，未來會提醒自己在網絡留言要更加謹慎。為了展現誠意，他還捐出一個月薪金給幾個慈善團體，希望事情盡快圓滿結束。<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"05ccdf26a0bccc19154943e85b14b82712de1af3","tid":1833934,"uid":124180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"呢個都叫有找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自殺嗰個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8a0cdadc56bbc2bdb642290a912971cc2addad","tid":1833934,"uid":28970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05ccdf26a0bccc19154943e85b14b82712de1af3","tid":1833934,"uid":124180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"呢個都叫有找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自殺嗰個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51Jug6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51Jug6W.jpg&h=c4f65705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78a305df550dd416c41e30a6c758711c4b8ee27c","tid":1833934,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"600 份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80a7a5d20673ded5c7661de7d1ea5aee1acd071","tid":1833934,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"睇咗做派雞捐精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73e9cec7dd31d5ed0be458b4c69531dd7d94736","tid":1833934,"uid":174601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d8a0cdadc56bbc2bdb642290a912971cc2addad","tid":1833934,"uid":28970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05ccdf26a0bccc19154943e85b14b82712de1af3","tid":1833934,"uid":124180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"呢個都叫有找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自殺嗰個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51Jug6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51Jug6W.jpg&h=c4f65705&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"死左回唔到"},{"pid":"bd3ef012edae51f23cf797b89360453dd2a629bd","tid":1833934,"uid":129385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b80a7a5d20673ded5c7661de7d1ea5aee1acd071","tid":1833934,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy"